{"tid":39609,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"梁 詠 琪 教 囡 囡 西 班 牙 過 聖 誕 習 俗","createTime":"2016-12-14T16:15:34.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-16T01:27:57.000Z","uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3606474046838350bc06abb3d58521dce0a1f683","tid":39609,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T16:15:34.000Z","msg":"梁詠琪 (GiGi) 為肩負生育重任，前年放慢工作步伐。囡囡Sofia轉眼成長，GiGi今年重開turbo，唱片、電影《骨妹》、配音動畫，緊接20周年巡迴演唱會，樂做兼顧家庭及演藝事業的超級媽咪。臨近聖誕，她終可放鬆一下，計劃出埠共度三口之家的第二個佳節，教開始懂事的囡囡西班牙過節習俗，「老公細個除咗會掛一隻襪，等聖誕老人擺禮物之外，臨瞓前會喺聖誕樹旁邊準備曲奇餅，同埋一杯奶。」老公深信為聖誕老人拉車的鹿會頸渴、肚餓，「如果起身見到俾人飲咗、食咗，證明聖誕老人嚟咗。當然都係爹哋、媽咪食㗎啦，但呢個都係佢細個嘅一個情懷，我哋都會做。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161213/large/1481626437_72ca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161213%2Flarge%2F1481626437_72ca.jpg&h=1c9f46e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nGiGi得到全家人無限量支持，在深圳首場巡唱，老公Sergio更匿在蛋糕內送驚喜。"},{"pid":"b87f1360fa7e4bae493dcdbe3ac64e96e8678a7f","tid":39609,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T16:18:17.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"c27a2e6f987c86f06fb4d56fc4ea2ea8027819b9","tid":39609,"uid":138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T16:26:45.000Z","msg":"西班牙籍"},{"pid":"785cef9e6db51c6b8db069c427eb6fe151da1e10","tid":39609,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T16:48:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df37b7fb50430eef71b85c9f64a0cddd0be94de6","tid":39609,"uid":43804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T00:30:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3830e3934407719f45e2c87d8ea108dd921aa0d","tid":39609,"uid":30022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T01:22:05.000Z","msg":"嗯"},{"pid":"162169e85319723089c51bbfd49cde602f72aa43","tid":39